##Работа с пользователями

***
####Получить список пользователей
```
curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" -X GET  http://{{ host }}/api/v1/users/list
```

####Создать пользователя
```
curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" -X POST -d '{"username":"{{ username }}","password":"34asasasj1","email":"{{ username }}@mail.ru"}' http://{{ host }}/api/v1/users/
```

####Отредактировать пользователя
```
curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}"  -X PUT -d '{"username":"New {{ username }}","password":"3433333j1","email":"{{ username }}@mail.ru"}' http://{{ host }}/api/v1/users/1
```

####Удалить пользователя
```
curl -i -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" -X DELETE http://{{ host }}/api/v1/users/1
```


##Работа с таблицами
***

####Создать таблицу
```
curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" -X POST -d '{"name":"MyTable","user_id":"{{ user_id }}"}' http://{{ host }}/api/v1/spreadsheets/
```

####Обновить таблицу
```
curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" -X PUT -d '{"name":"NewTable","user_id":"{{ user_id }}"}' http://{{ host }}/api/v1/spreadsheets/14
```
####Удалить таблицу
```
curl -i -H "Accept: application/json" -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" -X DELETE  http://{{ host }}/api/v1/spreadsheets/14
```


##Операции над значениями

***
###Создать или обновить ячейку
```
curl -i -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" -X POST -d '{"row":"1","column":"1","value":"15","user_id":"{{ user_id }}"}' http://{{ host }}/api/v1/spreadsheets/1/cells
```

###Удалить ячейку
```
curl -i -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" -X PUT -d '{"row":"1","column":"1","user_id":"{{ user_id }}"}' http://{{ host }}/api/v1/spreadsheets/1/cells
```

###Получить диапазон ячеек
```
curl -i -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" "http://{{ host }}/api/v1/spreadsheets/1/range_of_cells?start_range=1,1:10,15&horizontal_offset=1&vertical_offset=1&user_id={{ user_id }}&"
```

###Вычислить сумму
####По строке
```
curl -i -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" "http://{{ host }}/api/v1/spreadsheets/1/rows/sum?user_id={{ user_id }}&row_index=1"
```

####По столбцу
```
curl -i -H "X-AUTH-TOKEN: {{ token }}" "http://{{ host }}/api/v1/spreadsheets/1/columns/sum?user_id={{ user_id }}&column_index=1"
```

###Вычислить среднее
